ef=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Scheme.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme\">Scheme</a></span></div></div>","info":{"doc":"","docLink":"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Gluing.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData.toGlueData","kind":"def","line":90,"name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData.toGlueData","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Gluing.lean#L90-L91"}},{"header":"<div class=\"decl_header\"><span class=\"decl_kind\">structure</span>\n<span class=\"decl_name\"><a class=\"break_within\" href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Gluing.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData\"><span class=\"name\">AlgebraicGeometry</span>.<span class=\"name\">Scheme</span>.<span class=\"name\">GlueData</span></a></span><span class=\"decl_extends\">extends</span> <span class=\"fn\"><a href=\"./Mathlib/CategoryTheory/GlueData.html#CategoryTheory.GlueData\">CategoryTheory.GlueData</a> <a href=\"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Scheme.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme\">AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme</a></span><span class=\"decl_args\"> :</span><div class=\"decl_type\"><a href=\"./foundational_types.html\">Type</a> (u_1 + 1)</div></div>","info":{"doc":"A family of gluing data consists of\n1. An index type `J`\n2. A scheme `U i` for each `i : J`.\n3. A scheme `V i j` for each `i j : J`.\n  (Note that this is `J × J → Scheme` rather than `J → J → Scheme` to connect to the\n  limits library easier.)\n4. An open immersion `f i j : V i j ⟶ U i` for each `i j : ι`.\n5. A transition map `t i j : V i j ⟶ V j i` for each `i j : ι`.\nsuch that\n6. `f i i` is an isomorphism.\n7. `t i i` is the identity.\n8. `V i j ×[U i] V i k ⟶ V i j ⟶ V j i` factors through `V j k ×[U j] V j i ⟶ V j i` via some\n    `t' : V i j ×[U i] V i k ⟶ V j k ×[U j] V j i`.\n9. `t' i j k ≫ t' j k i ≫ t' k i j = 𝟙 _`.\n\nWe can then glue the schemes `U i` together by identifying `V i j` with `V j i`, such\nthat the `U i`'s are open subschemes of the glued space.\n","docLink":"./Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Gluing.html#AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData","kind":"structure","line":72,"name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData","sourceLink":"https://github.com/leanprover-community/mathlib4/blob/0f1dd7505c3d08b5feb82300ccc73179a457bf51/Mathlib/AlgebraicGeometry/Gluing.lean#L72-L91"}}],"imports":["Init","Mathlib.AlgebraicGeometry.Restrict","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.LocallyDirected","Mathlib.CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.Local","Mathlib.Geometry.RingedSpace.PresheafedSpace.Gluing"],"instances":[{"className":"AlgebraicGeometry.PresheafedSpace.IsOpenImmersion","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData.instIsOpenImmersionFLocallyRingedSpaceToLocallyRingedSpaceGlueData","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.GlueData.f"]},{"className":"AlgebraicGeometry.PresheafedSpace.IsOpenImmersion","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData.instIsOpenImmersionCommRingCatFSheafedSpaceToSheafedSpaceGlueDataToLocallyRingedSpaceGlueData","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.GlueData.f"]},{"className":"AlgebraicGeometry.PresheafedSpace.IsOpenImmersion","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData.instIsOpenImmersionCommRingCatFPresheafedSpaceToPresheafedSpaceGlueDataToSheafedSpaceGlueDataToLocallyRingedSpaceGlueData","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.GlueData.f"]},{"className":"AlgebraicGeometry.PresheafedSpace.IsOpenImmersion","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData.instIsOpenImmersionιLocallyRingedSpaceToLocallyRingedSpaceGlueData","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.GlueData.ι"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.CreatesColimit","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData.instCreatesColimitLocallyRingedSpaceWalkingMultispanProdJMultispanDiagramForgetToLocallyRingedSpace","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.Limits.MultispanIndex.multispan","AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.forgetToLocallyRingedSpace"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.Limits.PreservesColimit","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData.instPreservesColimitTopCatWalkingMultispanProdJMultispanDiagramForgetToTop","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.Limits.MultispanIndex.multispan","AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.forgetToTop"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.Limits.PreservesColimit","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData.instPreservesColimitWalkingMultispanProdJMultispanDiagramForget","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.Limits.MultispanIndex.multispan","AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.forget"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.Limits.HasColimit","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData.instHasMulticoequalizerDiagram","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.GlueData.diagram"]},{"className":"AlgebraicGeometry.PresheafedSpace.IsOpenImmersion","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.GlueData.ι_isOpenImmersion","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.GlueData.ι"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.IsIso","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.Cover.instIsIsoCommRingCatStalkMapFromGlued","typeNames":["AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.Hom.stalkMap"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.Epi","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.Cover.instEpiTopCatBaseCommRingCatFromGlued","typeNames":["AlgebraicGeometry.PresheafedSpace.Hom.base"]},{"className":"AlgebraicGeometry.PresheafedSpace.IsOpenImmersion","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.Cover.instIsOpenImmersionFromGlued","typeNames":["AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.Cover.fromGlued"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.IsIso","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.Cover.instIsIsoFromGlued","typeNames":["AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.Cover.fromGlued"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.IsLocalAtTarget","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.instIsLocalAtTargetIsomorphismsZariskiPrecoverage","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.MorphismProperty.isomorphisms","AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.zariskiPrecoverage"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.Limits.HasColimit","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.IsLocallyDirected.instHasColimit","typeNames":[]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.Limits.PreservesColimit","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.IsLocallyDirected.instPreservesColimitLocallyRingedSpaceForgetToLocallyRingedSpace","typeNames":["AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.forgetToLocallyRingedSpace"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.CreatesColimit","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.IsLocallyDirected.instCreatesColimitLocallyRingedSpaceForgetToLocallyRingedSpace","typeNames":["AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.forgetToLocallyRingedSpace"]},{"className":"AlgebraicGeometry.PresheafedSpace.IsOpenImmersion","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.IsLocallyDirected.instIsOpenImmersionι","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.Limits.colimit.ι"]},{"className":"CategoryTheory.Functor.IsLocallyDirected","name":"AlgebraicGeometry.Scheme.IsLocallyDirected.instIsLocallyDirectedWidePushoutShapeCompForgetOfIsOpenImmersionMap","typeNames":["CategoryTheory.Functor.comp"]}],"name":"Mathlib.AlgebraicGeometry.Gluing"}